snippet.title: Income Tax Officials Raid Jewellers Showroom in Chandigarh

localized.description:
Note Ban: Income Tax officials raids jewellers showroom in Chandigarh. Many jewellers have sold the gold and jewellery worth crores after demonetisation of Rs 500 and Rs 1000 notes.
Hundreds of crores have been seized in income tax raids across the country after demonetisation. On the other hand people are struggling to withdraw cash even after waiting for hours in queues outside banks and ATMs.
